### ============================================================
### D — POST /members/{id}/payments
### ============================================================

### D-1. Cas nominal — 201 Created — Paiement en espèces (CASH)
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{validMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 5000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId1}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{cashAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "CASH"
  }
]

###

### D-2. Cas nominal — 201 Created — Paiement Mobile Banking
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{validMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 10000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId2}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{mobileAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "MOBILE_BANKING"
  }
]

###

### D-3. Cas nominal — 201 Created — Paiement Virement bancaire
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{validMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 15000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId3}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{bankAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "BANK_TRANSFER"
  }
]

###

### D-4. Cas nominal — 201 Created — Plusieurs paiements en une requête
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{validMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 5000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId1}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{cashAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "CASH"
  },
  {
    "amount": 10000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId2}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{mobileAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "MOBILE_BANKING"
  }
]

###

### D-5. Erreur 404 — Membre inexistant
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{invalidMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 5000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId1}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{cashAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "CASH"
  }
]

###

### D-6. Erreur 400 — Montant négatif
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{validMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": -1000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId1}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{cashAccountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "CASH"
  }
]

###

### D-7. Erreur 400 — Champs obligatoires manquants
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{validMemberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 5000
  }
]

